    "description": "<p><em><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Specializations: </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Type of melee weapon used.</span></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Melee parry </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">is the &ldquo;reaction skill&rdquo; used if a character has a melee weapon and is attacked by someone with a </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">melee combat or</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">brawling</span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">attack. (Melee parry can&rsquo;t be used to parry projectile attacks &mdash; that&rsquo;s&nbsp;</span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">dodge.</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">)</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">If your character is defending against someone who is unarmed and doesn&rsquo;t have sharp natural weapons, the defender gets a +5 bonus modifier to his </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">melee parry </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">roll.</span><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">&nbsp;(REUP P90)</span></p>",
